{"id":174224,"type":1,"name":"流星傘下","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/12/6f/174224_FS5oV.jpg","summary":"　　这是个众星不断陨落，地面变得无法居住的世界。这里有着被称为天幕的存在，他可以用吐息在天空张开帷幕，借此挡下降星。在天幕‧德拉赛那的庇护下，人们开始在地面筑城生活。但德拉赛那与人类不同，活过了悠久的时光，并对此感到寂寞——","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>流星伞下</li><li><span>册数: </span>3</li><li><span>话数: </span>14</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/22472\">ミナヅキアキラ</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/128\">講談社</a>、<a href=\"/person/7033\">東立出版社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/19512\">少年マガジンエッジ</a></li><li><span>开始: </span>2016-03-17(2016年4月号)</li><li><span>结束: </span>2017-06-17(2017年7月号)</li>","collection":{"wish":3,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画","count":2},{"name":"漫画系列","count":1},{"name":"奇幻","count":1},{"name":"世界观","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":22472,"image":"","name":"ミナヅキアキラ","desc":"作者"},{"id":128,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2f/b1/128_prsn_nHh14.jpg","name":"讲谈社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7033,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fd/24/7033_prsn_J3N83.jpg","name":"东立出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":19512,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ac/4e/19512_prsn_9U92e.jpg","name":"少年マガジンエッジ","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":190109,"name":"流星傘下 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/a0/ba/190109_jp.jpg"},{"id":210127,"name":"流星傘下 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/e3/23/210127_jp.jpg"},{"id":220845,"name":"流星傘下 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9c/67/220845_jp.jpg"}]}